[[div class="onto_memo"]]

To all available and willing Delta-T personnel out there: during our universe's test of multiverse-traversing technology, a critical failure has occurred, resulting in drastic damage to local and multiversal reality. Consequently, a total of three of our local personnel -- two biological and one digital -- have become stranded across the Multiversal Compass.

I attach all relevant documentation below, but suffice to say their very existence within the myriad realities they could have ended up in is enough to destabilize entire timelines. By the power given to me by the 1981 Multi-Foundation Coalition Agreement, I hereby call upon all available Wardens to intervene as quickly as possible, before it becomes too late.

May the Irreal forgive us for our mistakes.

[[=]]
**-- James Micheals, Department of Ontokinetics, Director, TL-1911**
[[/=]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

